Package: mfcurve
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Factor Curve Analysis for Grouped Data in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel", "Krähmer", email = "Daniel.Kraehmer@soziologie.uni-muenchen.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Maximilian", "Frank", email = "maximilian.frank@psy.lmu.de", role = "aut"),
    person("Claudia", "Weileder", email = "claudia.weileder@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Daniel Krähmer <Daniel.Kraehmer@soziologie.uni-muenchen.de>
Description: Provides functions for multi-factor curve analysis, replicating and
    extending the functionality of the Stata mfcurve ado. Includes data preprocessing,
    statistical testing, and visualization of results with confidence intervals.
